description: Dinner on the table in 15 minutes? Yes please. This quick Mexican-inspired chicken salad is ready in no time.
keywords: Chicken salad,Low saturated fat,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Low sugar,Sesame free,High protein,High fibre,Soy free,Chicken,Dinner Made Easy,Peanut free
name: Fast Mexican Chicken Salad Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place chicken in a medium bowl with taco seasoning and toss to combine.
Heat a large saucepan over mediumhigh heat and add the olive oil. Add chicken to pan and cook for 4-5 minutes, stirring occasionally, until browned.
Add the corn and cook for a further 5 minutes, or until corn is lightly charred and chicken is cooked through.
In a bowl, toss the coleslaw together with the dressing from the kit, and divide among bowls. Top with chicken and corn, and sprinkle over the crumbled feta from the kit to serve.
